de.adorsys.datasafe.storage.api.actions

Interface StorageWriteService

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    StorageService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatabaseStorageService, FileSystemStorageService, S3StorageService, SchemeDelegatingStorage
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface StorageWriteService
    Raw file write operation at a given location. Paths use URL-encoding.

      • write

        OutputStream write(WithCallback<AbsoluteLocation,? extends ResourceWriteCallback> locationWithCallback)
        Parameters:
        locationWithCallback - absolute bucket path with credentials (if necessary) plus callbacks to be executed when file is written, i.e. notify callee that we assigned some file version
        Returns:
        data stream of resource to write to
